{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b4a971e16a","title":"中宣部转发西南局宣传部关于清反霸报道问题的意见的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3d6aa43059","index":0,"year":1950,"month":12,"day":19,"articleId":"b4a971e16a"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ee6892f2d1","type":"title","text":"中宣部转发西南局宣传部关于清能反霸报道问题的意见的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b4a971e16a"},{"id":"0c1bfdfcb7","type":"paragraph","text":"华东局、中南局、西北局宣传部，并转各分局、各省市区党委宣传部：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b4a971e16a"},{"id":"9e94c39d33","type":"paragraph","text":"兹将西南局宣传部对重庆《新华日报》关于报道土改和镇压反革命等方面的检讨发给你们。请对你们的报纸亦加以检讨。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b4a971e16a"},{"id":"5fe120495d","type":"paragraph","text":"中央宣传部","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b4a971e16a"},{"id":"d74cdd6d62","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b4a971e16a"},{"id":"505718e791","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]指中共中央西南局宣传部1950年12月15日关于重庆《新华日报》等在报道工作中存在的问题给所属各省区党委及宣传部并报中宣部的电报。这个电报指出，重庆《新华日报》等在关于清反霸、减租退押的报道中，不加选择，不分轻重，不管经验是否成熟，连篇累牌刊载这些方面的消息，在报纸上造成了一种非常紧张的空气。这种做法对于分化、孤立、麻敌人有害无益，很不策略，而且容易使实际工作发生偏向，希望各地引起注意。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b4a971e16a"}],"page":{"id":"5f4dfffed2","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b4a971e16a","start":449,"end":449}}}},"__N_SSG":true}